data.description: Great curb appeal! Just refreshed and excellent condition with one owner. The exterior of this home just got a fresh coat of paint in beautiful neutrals and a navy front door. The windows were professional cleaned inside and out, and all of the flooring has been updated with new carpet and engineered vinyl. This property also boasts an uncovered, fenced and paved side carport. You will enjoy being so close to town on this quiet dead end street with no neighbors to the back or to the west of this property. This 3 bed, 2.5 bath home is ready to meet its new family.
